name: Sports car
details: With this lovely Ariel singing doll, your little one can be part of both worlds brought to life in Disney's The Little Mermaid live action film. With a stunning character likeness, the doll comes with a flowing tail skirt as well as a pretty outfit that includes a dress, shoes and hair ribbon. The perfect inspiration for hours of play, this special doll sings a song from the film to spark and delight the imagination.
